metadata.title: Stesha Party Adult Wrapping Paper for Valentines Day, Birthday, Anniversary, Holiday, Gag Gift - Folded Flat 30 x 20 Inch (3 Sheets)
features: Use this funny adult themed wrapping paper to wrap your Valentine's Day, wedding, bachelorette, holiday, birthday, and gag gifts!
Vibrant colors printed on thick premium 70-lb glossy paper
3 Folded Flat Sheets of Premium Gift Wrapping Paper
Each flat sheet measures 30 inch x 20 inch = 12.5 sq ft of paper
description: The look and feel of this gift wrap is amazing! It is printed with vibrant colors on heavyweight premium 70-lb glossy paper that is thick and smooth to the touch. Sold in a 3-pack of folded flat sheets, each sheet measures 30" x 20" in size, for a total of 12.5 square feet of wrapping paper. Use this funny adult themed wrapping paper to wrap your Valentine's Day, wedding, bachelorette, holiday, birthday, and gag gifts!
